textBeforeTable: Annual tuitions are reported at the bachelor's level when available, and if not, at the master's level. Please view our full methodology here. This list of the 25 most affordable schools offering online nursing degrees presents economical options for students looking for nursing training online. Some of these options are for RN to BSN degree programs, others are for those interested in graduate degrees, such as a master's in nursing education or an advanced DNP degree. The cost of annual tuition costs for these programs starts at just $5,490, and all of the schools listed here report annual tuition costs of less than $15,000. 77% of users found this page helpful Was this page helpful?
